### Get all personal questions (NEW)
GET {{baseUrl}}/question-bank/new
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all personal questions
GET {{baseUrl}}/question-bank
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all personal questions in a category
GET {{baseUrl}}/question-bank/C%23
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Save new question
POST {{baseUrl}}/question-bank
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "category": "JavaScript",
    "question": "What is the significance of, and reason for, wrapping the entire content of a JavaScript source file in a function block?",
    "tags": ["fundamentals"],
    "time": 5
}

### Update question

PUT {{baseUrl}}/question-bank
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "questionId": "7bab9df9-3b35-4661-a8a4-03c6fa6aeb98",
    "category": "JavaScript",
    "question": "Can you name two programming paradigms important for JavaScript app developers?",
    "tags": ["concepts"],
    "time": 5
}

### Delete question

@questionId = 7bab9df9-3b35-4661-a8a4-03c6fa6aeb98

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/question-bank/{{questionId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}